flowRoot.flowPara: As a user, I want to have an account with money
in it
As an admin, I want to set the initial amount in
the money account
As an admin, I want to be able to set initial prices
of some items
As a user, I want the prices of items to change
over time and at different locations
As a user I want a spaceship which can hold cargo
As a user, I want to be able to upgrade my spaceship
As a user, I want to be able to buy a different spaceship
with different capabilities
As a user, I want a high score table
As a user, I want the game to end after a fixed amount of
time or turns
As a user, I want some visual representation of the universe
and a spaceship
As a user, I want to be able to save my progress
As a user I want to be able to play against other people
All the objects will have a graphic method
AI, may have a role in working the Economy System
As a user, I want to be able to fly to different
parts of the universe
As a user, I want to be able to buy and sell items
Referenced in the database
